{"tid":870360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永清完成維港渡海泳","createTime":"2018-10-21T05:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T05:34:04.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f05167c2716aa8e4d8815a41d8d02da7b2f2f0","tid":870360,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1995297/org/3ca2aaae5f1327eb9bc583fbdbb189a1.jpg/DNnxc17TtEMCI6Dcb7pfXxolcNRCk69moakV9aGpFfU?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1995297%2Forg%2F3ca2aaae5f1327eb9bc583fbdbb189a1.jpg%2FDNnxc17TtEMCI6Dcb7pfXxolcNRCk69moakV9aGpFfU%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=5d040b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n施永青自1976年已參加渡海泳<br />\n<br />\n自1976年起便參加維港泳前身的渡海泳，施永青憶述多年前比賽「以前污水直接流入個海到，真係試過游維港既時候，有米田共喺個海到漂吓漂吓，但而家個海（維港）真係乾淨咗好多。」<br />\n<br />\n他續指，自己於維港泳前3個月，已有到泳池和泳灘進行習泳訓練，為是日比賽做好準備。施永青笑言自己年紀不少，並沒有為比賽設定目標，只期望能順利完成賽事，享受維港兩岸景色。"},{"pid":"56524b4aad4ebe2cb3ad72cea914643289db7249","tid":870360,"uid":37528,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"6dd6589478187222b009447b025ef07125ea8f14","tid":870360,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:24:14.000Z","msg":"施永青：內地刁民已被縱壞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/858740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/858740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dc39f3ad6859e168e270034db7d30ef14b2c4ed","tid":870360,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:24:39.000Z","msg":"目測38B"},{"pid":"f1ca06e044507d274488f239a283ceba4f5f1e33","tid":870360,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"施永青：美已視中國 為敵對國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/868862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/868862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1cb022b6b62c63c27137fa15df57c9e9f4bfd006","tid":870360,"ui